WEBVTT

00:01.040 --> 00:02.439
<i>Previously on</i> One Tree Hill.

00:02.520 --> 00:03.714
I'm your mother.

00:03.800 --> 00:07.713
- Is this woman my mother?
- Your mom is gone, Peyton.

00:07.800 --> 00:10.872
But your biological mother is alive.

00:11.880 --> 00:14.713
<i>I saw her buying drugs in the park today.</i>
<i>I'm sorry.</i>

00:15.040 --> 00:18.396
- You and Erica broke up?
- She got popular.

00:18.480 --> 00:19.515
I love you.

00:19.600 --> 00:21.875
I really don't know
when I'm gonna be ready for us again,

00:21.960 --> 00:24.030
or even if I'll be ready for us at all.

00:24.120 --> 00:27.510
We could totally have a summer-like fling,
just in the fall.

00:27.600 --> 00:29.955
And nonexclusive.

00:30.840 --> 00:33.115
I'm the guy for you, Brooke Davis.

00:33.320 --> 00:34.435
You'll see.

00:34.520 --> 00:37.080
<i>Three months ago,</i>
<i>someone tried to kill me.</i>

00:37.160 --> 00:40.197
<i>And when I find out who did this to me,</i>
<i>and I will find out soon,</i>

00:40.280 --> 00:43.590
<i>the sins I commit then</i>
<i>could turn this place to rubble.</i>

00:45.000 --> 00:51.074
